Build a User CRUD WebService
a) Add a User (Register a New User Feature) . It Check the User is not already exist
Email , Password, Name , Phone
Mongoose Level Validations Need to be Add (Email must be Unique, Required and Well Format Email)
Password Must be >=8 and <=25
Name is Only Alphabet >=3 and <=25
Phone Must be 10 Digit Long.

Password Must Be Encrypted Store in DB 
Hint : Using Bcrypt

b) View User (View User Profile) Feature Based on Email

c) Update User Password (Set a New Password)

d) Delete a User Based on Email Id

All the WebServices are test on Post Man.

